- A Teddy Bear - Ice cream on arrival
- Organic Children Shampoo - Bathrobe and slippers for the stay
- Jelly beans - Parents London Survival Guide
- Wisdom toothbrush - Expert advice on family attractions in London
- Kids Room Service Items - Hotel Restaurant Children’s Menu
